      "content": "but there aren't any different paths. the map is complete. i've been looking at the terminal and thinking... if the trip is over, why stay at the station waiting for a train that isn't coming? it just seems more peaceful to just leave the station, leave it all behind, and stop trying to find meaning where there isn't any left.",
